overview.en: USDH (Huione USD) is a stable and digital currency issued by Huione Payment，and its value comes from the real assets of Huione and will always be equal to the USD , thus becoming a stable asset. Huione Payment will provide official exchange services and free markets for USDH, USD, and USDT.
overview.zh: USDH（Huione USD）是汇旺支付发行的稳定数字货币，其价值来源于汇旺的实体资产，永远与美元等值，成为稳定资产。汇旺支付将为USDH、USD、USDT提供官方兑换服务和自由市场.
